thread.title: Serge Sviridenko

author: Serge Sviridenko
title: Serge Sviridenko
text: Just placed my 4th order with them. We will continue using these guys for every prototype/emergency project our department is working on. These are professional quality boards at the fraction of the cost. Easy file upload and processing. Very quick turnaround, don't have to wait a month to get your boards. I hope they will offer more services and options in the future for more advanced board features.
